{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_05_01",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 ついに女優デビュー！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "成宮すず！　{user}さんの\n呼び出しに応じて、来てあげましたわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu Narumiya! I've come\nin response to your call‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……相変わらず元気だな\n忙しい中、来てもらってすまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Still full of energy‚ huh?\nYou're busy‚ yet you came. Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "他ならぬ{user}さんの呼び出しですもの\nそれに、打ち合わせも仕事のうちです。お気になさらず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's your call‚ {user}-san‚ not just anyone else's.\nAnd besides‚ meetings are a part of work. Don't worry about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、私に直接話したいことってなんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But more importantly‚ what kind of talk\ndid you want to have with me directly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4149431069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、仕事の話なんだけど……今までと違うタイプの\n仕事だから、直接説明した方がいいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's about our schedule… It's something different from\nwhat we've done so far‚ so I thought I'd discuss it with you directly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "今までと違うお仕事、ですって？\n……ふっ、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something different from what we've done so far?\n…Heh‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私はもう駆け出しの新人アイドルでは\nありませんわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not just a rookie idol\nwho debuted not too long ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9419503212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロを背負って立つ『二代目星降る奇跡』\nこの成宮すずに、そんな気遣いは無用ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bear the title of \"Second Generation Starry Miracle\"\nfrom Hoshimi Production.\nYou don't need to worry about such things with me‚\nSuzu Narumiya.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "どんな仕事でも余裕でこなしてご覧に入れます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter what it is‚ I can handle it easily.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、なら良かった。あのな、実は……\nすずに連続テレビドラマの出演オファーがきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ then I can rest easy. Actually…\nI received an offer for you to appear in a TV drama.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、やっぱり私の想定内のお仕事ですわ\n――って連ドラの出演！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ it's within the realm of expectations.\n――A drama appearance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、人気ドラマで、確か今シーズン10が放送中だ\n毎回殺人事件が起きるんだよな。すずも知ってるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's a popular drama currently in its 10th season.\nThere's a murder case every time. You know that drama‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "それ、子供の頃から観ていますわ！\nわっ、わっ、私が出演……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I've been watching that since I was a child!\nM-Me‚ appearing…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ぜ、全国放送の有名連ドラ……\nしかも私が好きなあの作品で、女優デビュー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In a nationally broadcasted‚ famous drama…\nAnd to make it even better‚ it's a debut as an actress in a work I love!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すず、大丈夫か？　震えてるぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ are you okay? You seem shaky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、震えてませんわ！　さ、さすがにほんのちょっと\nわずかばかり、お、驚きましたけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm not shaking! I-It's just that‚\nwell‚ a tiny bit… I was a little surprised!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "役者の仕事は今回が初めてだけど、新しいファンを\n獲得出来るし、今後の活動の幅も広がると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is your first acting job‚ and I think you can gain new fans\nand expand the range of your future activities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でもまずは、すずの意向を聞きたい\n興味はあるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But first‚ I want to know your opinion‚ Suzu.\nAre you interested?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……。ついに演技の世界にも\n私の才能が伝わってしまったのですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… My talent for acting has\nfinally been recognized‚ it seems…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、日本のドラマの発展のため\n女優としてお力を貸したいのはやまやまなのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I'm very eager to contribute as\nan actress for the development of Japanese dramas…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "私、成宮すずは、麻奈様の後を継ぐ\n天才アイドルを目指す身",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ I‚ Suzu Narumiya‚ am striving to become\nthe successor to Mana-sama‚ aiming to be a genius idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルと女優との二足のわらじを履くべきでしょうか\nまだ時期尚早な気もしますわ……はぁ、悩ましい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Should I juggle being both an idol and an actress?\nIt might still be too early for that… Sigh‚ it's troubling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……そういうことならすずの気持ちを尊重するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… If that's the case‚ I'll respect your feelings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "ですけど、{user}さんが\nど～～してもと言うことでしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ {user}-san‚\nif you insist~~~~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "残念だけど、今回は見送ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a pity‚ but let's pass on this opportunity for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "ちょーーっとお待ちなさい！！\n諦めるのが早過ぎません！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait !!!! Just a moment!!\nIsn't giving up too quickly!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し熱心に説得したら、渋々\n「そんなに頼むなら仕方ありませんわね～」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you were a bit more persistent in persuading‚ I might reluctantly say\n\"If you're asking that much‚ I guess I can't refuse…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "――と折れるかもしれませんのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、ドラマに出たいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you saying you want to be in the drama?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz020.m4a",
